structure.unit: AGRICULTURAL SEEDS, FEEDING STUFFS, AND FERTILIZERS

law.history: Repealed 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 370, sec. 15, effective April 8, 1994. -- Created 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 2, sec. 1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Certification of seeds or plant parts produced outside Kentucky for sale within Kentucky, or produced within Kentucky for sale outside Kentucky.
